{"tid":1678431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可能你會覺得我係P牌撚，但好真心想話比大家知，因為831，我到今時今日都好大陰影訓唔著","createTime":"2019-10-27T16:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T06:37:26.000Z","uid":264609,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb84fa0821f27bf33a3d6737e3abdb6bbbdb88f","tid":1678431,"uid":264609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好想大家知道⋯⋯￼<br />\n<br />\n雖然我只系個P牌仔，不過呢個星期見到連登搞成咁，真系忍唔住開個post問下大家，你地系咪唔捻記得哂831？！<br />\n<br />\n一個二個比三毛五毛帶哂，行動post呢？行動post呢？<br />\n<br />\n721出事<br />\n821悼念<br />\n921悼念<br />\n1021悼念<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>831出事<br />\n去到1031只不過兩個月咋！<br />\n<br />\n你地已經唔捻記得哂！？<br />\n仲柴娃娃去蘭桂坊面具夜￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n10月31號太子悼念831兩個月竟然一個post都無提過！</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n系咪慣左太子晚晚有人拜就唔捻理？<br />\n系咪慣左一個月悼念咗，第二個月就唔捻理？<br />\n系咪慣左藍旗黑旗出TG就唔捻去？￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n對唔住各位手足，我真心忍唔住要出post屌下<br />\n文宣做得甘辛苦為乜</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HLnqSXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHLnqSXO.jpg&h=95b2490e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3hKo4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3hKo4u.jpg&h=236cd3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/te0cxXP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fte0cxXP.jpg&h=118cf232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QJ2aKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QJ2aKy.png&h=35ea4cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FBod1Rg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFBod1Rg.jpg&h=8a6413e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nusa34C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNusa34C.jpg&h=edc2ae29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">10月31號<br />\n夜晚七點<br />\n太子靈堂見</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n手足幫手推出去"},{"pid":"57bf881c172053b10ac780c5ec4a0993d4b9c3b3","tid":1678431,"uid":84308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"721 唔見人<br />\n831 打死人<br />\n101 槍殺人"},{"pid":"3ccb54611bb0bfb8cc5d02052f5008c2248efb53","tid":1678431,"uid":14070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f706885637df359dedf8cc302439d62b18b8e326","tid":1678431,"uid":114360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1CqSY2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1CqSY2.gif&h=b85b3ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫手推post<br />\n已經整整兩個月 黨鐵冇比過市民任何交代<br />\n我地唔可以忘記！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8b74d2ee81fefd87f15a2e9497dbc525d4e2ed","tid":1678431,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168d1efa07fc439a3ff6235dede1962653cfa86a","tid":1678431,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"邊撚個話唔記得"},{"pid":"637d416b127e30283c98da166beb0906475599f5","tid":1678431,"uid":38157,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nbtw系完未"},{"pid":"a4a1d3668026b517d587d9856fc1d49cb0377722","tid":1678431,"uid":88773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2