owdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=ec984835\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=7870b44d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4cpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=e7d92056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>區議會選舉經費大籌集</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678412/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678412/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d56302c715e7aac9731fc495ae1da7c9af046d8a","tid":1678431,"uid":82452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srDYtzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrDYtzR.jpg&h=a4a21cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFWGrmx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFWGrmx.jpg&h=fb17a103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQGSx1y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQGSx1y.jpg&h=ddc0b2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkV4o8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkV4o8f.jpg&h=5ff1f5b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb85d0209aca7d7e15cf69bee22b0724f70bdd82","tid":1678431,"uid":147425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"10月31日7PM太子站見呀大家<br />\n唔好忘記喺831受傷同死去既手足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6f2b1fce07ac3a8bae2fd3b0d7705e326983fa","tid":1678431,"uid":109047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n1031太子見"},{"pid":"703c5794912c542f466e9a5c780e5b458d887a7e","tid":1678431,"uid":264609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"今日見尖沙咀又9拉左百幾個手足<br />\n又訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/